name: Void Swinger 64
description:
This game is based off of the classic N64 gaming console that came out in 1996 and was responsible for some of the best 3d platform games to ever exist,

Plot:

You play as a survivor after a dimension shattering event occurs, swing your way through the Void as you attempt to get back home...

This game was made in part as a submission to the:

Diving Squid Community Jam.
